Dependency Information

Apache Maven

  <groupId>org.cruk.genologics</groupId>
  <artifactId>clarity-client</artifactId>
  <version>2.26.1</version>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'org.cruk.genologics:clarity-client:jar:2.26.1'

Apache Ivy

<dependency org="org.cruk.genologics" name="clarity-client" rev="2.26.1">

</dependency>

Groovy Grape

)

Gradle/Grails

Scala SBT
